<span id="cb8-8"><a href="#cb8-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                <span class="op">&gt;&gt;=</span> loadAndApplyTemplate <span class="st">&quot;templates/default.html&quot;</span> (mathCtx <span class="op">&lt;&gt;</span> defaultContext)</span>
<span id="cb8-9"><a href="#cb8-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                <span class="op">&gt;&gt;=</span> relativizeUrls</span></code></pre></div>
<h1 data-number="5" id="目次の生成"><span class="header-section-number">5</span> 目次の生成</h1>
<p><a href="https://svejcar.dev/posts/2019/11/27/table-of-contents-in-hakyll/">こちらのサイト</a>そのままで導入した.
だんだんPandocのOptionが長くなっていく…</p>
<div class="sourceCode" id="cb9"><pre class="sourceCode haskell"><code class="sourceCode haskell"><span id="cb9-1"><a href="#cb9-1" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">import</span>           <span class="dt">Prelude</span></span>
<span id="cb9-2"><a href="#cb9-2" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="kw">import</span>           <span class="dt">Data.Functor.Identity</span> (runIdentity)</span>
<span id="cb9-3"><a href="#cb9-3" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb9-4"><a href="#cb9-4" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>tocTemplate <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="fu">either</span> <span class="fu">error</span> Prelude.id <span class="op">.</span> runIdentity <span class="op">.</span> Pandoc.compileTemplate <span class="st">&quot;&quot;</span> <span class="op">$</span> T.unlines</span>
<span id="cb9-5"><a href="#cb9-5" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  [ <span class="st">&quot;&lt;div class=\&quot;toc\&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=\&quot;header\&quot;&gt;Table of Contents&lt;/div&gt;&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb9-6"><a href="#cb9-6" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  , <span class="st">&quot;$toc$&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb9-7"><a href="#cb9-7" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  , <span class="st">&quot;&lt;/div&gt;&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb9-8"><a href="#cb9-8" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  , <span class="st">&quot;$body$&quot;</span></span>
<span id="cb9-9"><a href="#cb9-9" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>  ]</span>
<span id="cb9-10"><a href="#cb9-10" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a></span>
<span id="cb9-11"><a href="#cb9-11" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a><span class="ot">customWriterOptions::</span> <span class="dt">Pandoc.WriterOptions</span></span>
<span id="cb9-12"><a href="#cb9-12" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>customWriterOptions <span class="ot">=</span> defaultHakyllWriterOptions</span>
<span id="cb9-13"><a href="#cb9-13" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        { Pandoc.writerHTMLMathMethod   <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dt">Pandoc.MathJax</span> <span class="st">&quot;&quot;</span>       <span class="co">-- LaTeX</span></span>
<span id="cb9-14"><a href="#cb9-14" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        , Pandoc.writerNumberSections   <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dt">True</span></span>
<span id="cb9-15"><a href="#cb9-15" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        , Pandoc.writerHighlightStyle   <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dt">Just</span> pandocCodeStyle    <span class="co">-- Syntax</span></span>
<span id="cb9-16"><a href="#cb9-16" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        , Pandoc.writerTableOfContents  <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dt">True</span>                    <span class="co">-- toc</span></span>
<span id="cb9-17"><a href="#cb9-17" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        , Pandoc.writerTOCDepth         <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dv">3</span></span>
<span id="cb9-18"><a href="#cb9-18" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        , Pandoc.writerTemplate          <span class="ot">=</span> <span class="dt">Just</span> tocTemplate</span>
<span id="cb9-19"><a href="#cb9-19" aria-hidden="true" tabindex="-1"></a>                        }</span></code></pre></div>
